    "ron_burgundy_voice": "Well, folks, it appears we witnessed a rather\u2026 prolonged exchange of the pickleball. A true test of endurance, if you will. One player, in a moment of what I can only describe as 'net-adjacent confusion,' decided to gift the ball to the opposition. Stay classy, pickleball fans.",
